title: QuinStreet: Fiscal 3Q Earnings Snapshot
text:
FOSTER CITY, Calif. (AP) _ QuinStreet Inc. (QNST) on Wednesday reported fiscal third-quarter profit of $7.1 million.
The Foster City, California-based company said it had profit of 14 cents per share. Earnings, adjusted for one-time gains and costs, came to 16 cents per share.
The online marketing services company posted revenue of $117.9 million in the period.
QuinStreet shares have climbed 39 percent since the beginning of the year. The stock has more than doubled in the last 12 months.
